      </div>

      <div id="question9" class="question-container">
        <h1>Question 9</h1>
        <p>Consider the following statement and indicate whether it is TRUE or FALSE.</p>
        <p>The first step of managing cashflow is to determine how much cash is coming into the business and how much the business has at any point in time.</p>
        <select name="q9" id="">
        <option value="" selected disabled hidden>SELECT OPTION</option>
        <option value="true">True</option>
        <option value="false">False</option>
        </select>
      </div>

      <div id="question10" class="question-container">
        <h1>Question 10</h1>
        <p>Consider the following statement and indicate whether it is TRUE or FALSE.</p>
        <p>Business insurance is used by the businesses to transfer the risk they face to an insurance company by paying the insurance company a premium.</p>
        <select name="q10" id="">
            <option value="" selected disabled hidden>SELECT OPTION</option>
            <option value="true">True</option>
            <option value="false">False</option>
        </select>
      </div>

      <div id="question11" class="question-container">
        <h1>Please provide your ID number, as well as your Name and Surname for your Certificate of completion.</h1>
        <!-- ID/passport number insert field -->
        <input type="text" name="id_number" id="id_number" placeholder="ID/Passport Number" maxlength="13" required>
        <!-- <input type="text" name="name_surname" id="name_surname" placeholder="Name & Surname" maxlength="13" required> -->
      </div>
      <!-- hidden attributes -->
      <input type="hidden" name="phoneNumber" id="phoneNumber" value="<%- number %>"/>
  </form>
  <button id="prev_btn">Previous</button>
  <button id="next_btn">Next</button>
  <button id="submit_btn" type="button">Submit</button>

  <div id="failed_quiz_div" class="question-container">
    <h1>Quiz not passed</h1>
    <p>Unfortunately you didn't pass the quiz, you can retry the quiz to get your certificate</p>
    <p>You got <span id="quiz_result"></span>/10</p>
    <button id="restart_training_vid">Rewatch Video</button>
    <button id="restart_quiz">Restart Quiz</button>
   </div>
  <div id="succesful_quiz_div" class="question-container">
    <h1>You Passed</h1>
    <p>Congratulations you passed the quiz by getting <span class="quiz_result"></span>/10.</p>
    <p>You will recieve your certificate via a message shortly.</p>
